OL,3,C'Paedophile hunter' jailed over racist
OL,4,Cchants and gestures at protest
OL,6,FA self-styled paedophile hunter who
OL,7,Fmocked Muslim prayer and shouted
OL,8,Fracist slurs at a protest in Leeds has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FPhilip Hoban, one of the founder
OL,12,Fmembers of an online group called
OL,13,FPredator Exposure UK, was prosecuted
OL,14,Ffor his involvement in demonstrations
OL,15,Fon The Headrow on 3 August.
OL,17,FThe incident happened as far-right
OL,18,Fprotesters clashed with an anti-racism
OL,19,Fgroup outside Leeds Art Gallery.
