OL,3,C'Paedophile hunter' jailed over racist
OL,4,Cchants and gestures at protest
OL,6,FHoban, 48, was seen making racist
OL,7,Fgestures to rival protesters.
OL,9,FHe admitted racially aggravated
OL,10,Fthreatening behaviour.
OL,12,FAt Leeds Crown Court on Thursday, 15
OL,13,FAugust, footage of Hoban was shown to
OL,14,Fthe Recorder of Leeds, Judge Guy Kearl
OL,15,FKC, who described his actions as
OL,16,F"designed to stir up hatred."
OL,18,F"You climbed on to a barrier and
OL,19,Fstarted rubbing your lips towards a
OL,20,Fperson of colour," he said.
