OL,6,F"You were standing alongside, and in
OL,7,Fthe same group as, others who were
OL,8,Fmaking similarly racist and insulting
OL,9,Fgestures, some making monkey noises
OL,10,Fand gestures.
OL,12,F"You then started to imitate the
OL,13,Fmanner in which Muslim people pray, in
OL,14,Forder to mock their religion."
OL,16,FHe added that what Hoban had done
OL,17,Fcould not be "viewed in isolation" and
OL,18,Fshould be seen against the "background
OL,19,Fof unrest and disorder in the country."
