OL,6,FFollowing his arrest, Hoban took to
OL,7,Fhis social media to defend his
OL,8,Factions. In a series of videos on
OL,9,FTiktok he said: "I am mixed race, my
OL,10,Fkids are mixed race, my dad is black.
OL,11,FIt's got nothing to do with race
OL,12,Fwhatsoever.
OL,14,F"They were throwing banter at us, so
OL,15,Fwe were throwing it back.
OL,17,F"For all the people that say I'm
OL,18,Fracist, I'm far from it."
