OL,6,FRepresenting himself in court, Hoban,
OL,7,Fof Northcote Crescent, Beeston,
OL,8,Fclaimed Predator Exposure had helped
OL,9,Fto convict more than 400 predators.
OL,11,FThe group has a significant social
OL,12,Fmedia profile, with more than 500,000
OL,13,Ffollowers on Facebook.
