OL,6,FHoban admitted he had behaved like a
OL,7,F"stupid drunken idiot" and said he had
OL,8,Fstepped down from his role with the
OL,9,Fgroup because there "is no room for
OL,10,Ffools like me".
OL,12,FHe was sentenced to eight months in
OL,13,Fprison and a was given a five year
OL,14,FCriminal Behaviour Order.
OL,16,FFellow protester James Gettings was
OL,17,Falso jailed for eight months for his
OL,18,Fparts in the incident.
